{"id":282433,"type":2,"name":"映像研には手を出すな！","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/5f/18/282433_9wDx9.jpg","summary":"高中1年级学生浅草绿，是强调“设定即生命”的动画迷。在素描本上描绘积累各种各样的想法，却因不能一个人行动做事而无法迈出走向动画制作的一步。对于浅草这种才能，拥有制片人气质的金森沙耶香很快注意到了。同时，得知同学兼新星读者模特的水崎燕，其实希望将来成为动画人，3人为了展现脑内“最强的世界”而设立了映像研……","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>别对映像研出手！</li><li><span>话数: </span>*</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>2020年1月5日</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>星期日</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/24619\">大童澄瞳</a>（小学館「月刊！スピリッツ」連載中）</li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/2280\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">湯浅政明</a></li><li><span>脚本: </span><a href=\"/person/24593\">木戸雄一郎</a></li><li><span>分镜: </span><a href=\"/person/14725\">川畑喬</a>、<a href=\"/person/36260\">本橋茉里</a></li><li><span>演出: </span><a href=\"/person/2280\">湯浅政明</a>、<a href=\"/person/36260\">本橋茉里</a>、<a href=\"/person/24733\">殿水敦子</a></li><li><span>音乐: </span><a href=\"/person/15560\">オオルタイチ</a></li><li><span>人物设定: </span><a href=\"/person/12700\">浅野直之</a></li><li><span>系列构成: </span><a href=\"/person/2280\">湯浅政明</a></li><li><span>美术监督: </span><a href=\"/person/6801\">野村正信</a></li><li><span>色彩设计: </span><a href=\"/person/36225\">中村絢郁</a></li><li><span>作画监督: </span><a href=\"/person/13082\">寺尾憲治</a></li><li><span>摄影监督: </span><a href=\"/person/2344\">関谷能弘</a></li><li><span>原画: </span><a href=\"/person/11323\">松本憲生</a>、<a href=\"/person/35879\">Maring Song</a></li><li><span>剪辑: </span><a href=\"/person/26954\">齋藤朱里</a></li><li><span>系列监督: </span><a href=\"/person/31386\">大野勉</a></li><li><span>音响监督: </span><a href=\"/person/2577\">木村絵理子</a></li><li><span>制作助手: </span><a href=\"/person/11389\">D.R MOVIE</a></li><li><span>动画制作: </span><a href=\"/person/26100\">サイエンスSARU</a></li><li><span>副导演: </span><a href=\"/person/36260\">本橋茉里</a></li><li><span>OP・ED 分镜: </span><a href=\"/person/2280\">湯浅政明</a></li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://eizouken-anime.com/</li><li><span>播放电视台: </span>NHK総合テレビ</li><li><span>Copyright: </span>©2020 大童澄瞳・小学館／「映像研」製作委員会</li><li><span>主题歌演出: </span>chelmico / 神様、僕は気づいてしまった</li><li><span>企划: </span>川村明广、田边良成、汤浅政明、沢边伸政、vic horikiri</li><li><span>制片人: </span>鹤冈信哉、坂田淳、eunyoung choi、冈本顺哉</li><li><span>动画制片人: </span>eunyoung choi</li>","collection":{"wish":369,"collect":45,"doing":1741,"on_hold":16,"dropped":14},"tags":[{"name":"汤浅政明","count":310},{"name":"2020年1月","count":277},{"name":"TV","count":218},{"name":"ScienceSARU","count":194},{"name":"漫画改","count":153},{"name":"2020","count":121},{"name":"漫改","count":93},{"name":"湯浅政明","count":69},{"name":"校园","count":60},{"name":"青春","count":56},{"name":"日本动画","count":24},{"name":"Science_SARU","count":17},{"name":"伊藤沙莉","count":9},{"name":"2020年","count":6},{"name":"サイエンスSARU","count":4},{"name":"别对映像研出手！","count":4},{"name":"季番","count":4},{"name":"TVA","count":4},{"name":"动画制作","count":4},{"name":"日常","count":3},{"name":"神作","count":3},{"name":"浅野直之","count":3},{"name":"漫画改编","count":3},{"name":"大童澄瞳","count":3},{"name":"小松未可子","count":2},{"name":"田村睦心","count":2},{"name":"松岡美里","count":2},{"name":"2020冬","count":2},{"name":"本橋茉里","count":2},{"name":"木戸雄一郎","count":2}],"eps":[{"id":924371,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/924371","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"最強の世界！","name_cn":"最强的世界！","duration":"00:25:00","airdate":"2020-01-05","comment":109,"desc":"アニメーション制作を夢見る高校１年生の浅草みどりは、同級生の金森さやかとともにアニメ研の上映会へ。 すると、カリスマ読者モデルとして知られる水崎ツバメが声をかけてきた。水崎はなぜか黒ずくめの男たちに追われていた。 浅草と金森は彼女を助け、男たちを撃退する。そして２人は水崎が意外にもアニメーター志望であることを知る。 浅草と水崎の即興での合作が始まり、意気投合した３人の前に「最強の世界」が広がっていく…。\r\nMidori ASAKUSA is a first year high school student who dreams of creating her own animation. When she visits a screening event held by Anime Club with fellow student Sayaka KANAMORI, an amateur model Tsubasa MIZUSAKI starts talking to them. As she was being chased by men dressed in all black, ASAKUSA and KANAMORI help her get rid of them. To their surprise, they learn that MIZUSAKI is also aspiring to be an animator. The three of them hit it off to realize their own \"Incredible World\" together!\r\n\r\n分镜: 本桥茉里\r\n演出: 本桥茉里 , 汤浅政明\r\n作画监督: 大野勉 , 寺尾宪治\r\n机械作监: 寺尾宪治\r\n原画: 村上泉 , 榎本柊斗 , すごろく , 加藤祯一 , 松本宪生 , 田口爱梨 , 菅野一期 , 堀裕津 , 立花希望 , 永田有香 , 清水奏太郎 , moaang , Maring Song , 稻田有华 , 长滨佑作 , 前场健次","status":"Air"},{"id":924372,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/924372","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"映像研、爆誕す！","name_cn":"映像研，爆炸诞生！","duration":"00:25:00","airdate":"2020-01-12","comment":58,"desc":"水崎がアニメ研究部に入ることを親に禁じられているので、浅草・金森とともにアニメを作るには新しい部活を立ち上げるしかない。３人は職員室に向かう。既にアニ研があるため、アニメを作ると言うわけにはいかない。実写系の部活が教師に求められていることを知った金森は、映像部を名乗ってアニメを作ることを発案する。こうして「映像研」が爆誕した！そして３人がかつてアニ研が使っていたという倉庫を開けると、そこは宝の山？\r\nAs Mizusaki is banned from joining the anime club by her parents, the only way for the three of them to make anime is to set up a new club. At the staff room, their teacher tells them that they will be granted a certain budget if the objective of their club was to create a live-action movie. Kanamori suggest that they will call their club “Eizou (Film) club” and use its name as a disguise. Thus “ Eizou-ken” came into existence! They head off to a storage space previously used by the anime club and realized all kinds of treasures behind the door!\r\n\r\n絵コンテ：川畑　喬\r\n演出：殿水敦子\r\n作画監督：濱口　漠、森田　実、早乙女　啓(ムツプランニング)","status":"Air"},{"id":924373,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/924373","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2020-01-19","comment":1,"desc":"演出：五十嵐祐貴","status":"NA"},{"id":924374,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/924374","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2020-01-26","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":924375,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/924375","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2020-02-02","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":924376,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/924376","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2020-02-09","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":924377,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/924377","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"2020-02-16","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"NA"},{"id":924378,"